                <img class="event-img" src="/cmsstatic/asset/images/temp/event_558x310_1.jpg" alt="이미지명">
              </a>
              <div class="event-info">
                <p class="event-info__name">당신의 반려견에게 왕관을 씌워주세요!</p>
